https://github.com/taku-o/vim-fix-numbering

fix numbering.

------------------------------------------------------------
Command
    :[range]FixNumbering {number_index}


------------------------------------------------------------
Command Example.

    1. sample data is this.

        515 Allegra Gilbert 747 Sibelius 123 484 140
        764 Violet Elliott 935 Altavista 721 830 785
        979 Yoshi Noel 750 Lavasoft 542 636 567
        715 Portia Battle 918 Adobe 590 394 760
        845 Kimberly Watson 143 Chami 180 468 346
        829 Lael Dickson 560 Cakewalk 825 929 964
        870 Sierra Decker 690 Apple Systems 565 629 142
        588 Ursa Gonzales 173 Macromedia 744 408 708
        840 Phoebe Wong 521 Lycos 579 771 610
        137 Fatima Wade 468 Cakewalk 474 154 115
        515 Ariana Stuart 485 Sibelius 491 920 643
        459 Sage Bradshaw 198 Adobe 960 324 545

    2. execute 'FixNumbering' command.

        :%FixNumbering 4

    3. command result is this.
       numbering is fixed.

        515 Allegra Gilbert 747 Sibelius 123 484 140
        764 Violet Elliott 935 Altavista 721 485 785
        979 Yoshi Noel 750 Lavasoft 542 486 567
        715 Portia Battle 918 Adobe 590 487 760
        845 Kimberly Watson 143 Chami 180 488 346
        829 Lael Dickson 560 Cakewalk 825 489 964
        870 Sierra Decker 690 Apple Systems 565 490 142
        588 Ursa Gonzales 173 Macromedia 744 491 708
        840 Phoebe Wong 521 Lycos 579 492 610
        137 Fatima Wade 468 Cakewalk 474 493 115
        515 Ariana Stuart 485 Sibelius 491 494 643
        459 Sage Bradshaw 198 Adobe 960 495 545

